.TH microservice "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Base Command"
.SH NAME
microservice \- A simple infinite loop microservice example
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B microservice
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B microservice
is a simple shell script that runs an infinite loop, printing "Running infinite loop..." every second. It serves as an example or placeholder for a microservice.
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Junie.
